  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Need to check the price of an item or see your current on-hand quantity? Users can check this information no matter where they are in the system and without interrupting their current workflow.</p><h3 id=\"PriceChecksandOn-HandQuantities-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933705356/Getting+Started+The+RepairQ+Dashboard\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933705356\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Getting Started: The RepairQ Dashboard</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933672605/Getting+Started+The+RepairQ+Menu+Item+Bar\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933672605\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Getting Started: The RepairQ Menu Item Bar</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933705409/Getting+Started+The+RepairQ+Global+Search+Bar\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933705409\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Getting Started: The RepairQ Global Search Bar</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279488/Instructional%20-%200091cd.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"PriceChecksandOn-HandQuantities-PerformingaPriceCheckandCheckingOnhandQuantity\">Performing a Price Check and Checking Onhand Quantity</h2><p /><p>1. On the right side of the RepairQ Navigation Bar, click the <strong>Price Check</strong> button.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"566\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279488/Price%20Check%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. A Price Check pop-up window will appear. In the Search Box, you can type in a Keyword/SKU/UPC/Serial Number, then select a location to search. You can search any location where you have a role assigned. Click the <strong>Search</strong> button to submit.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279488/Price%20Check%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. Your search results will provide item information including the location, Instock quantity, Price, and Price+Tax.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279488/Price%20Check%205.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note:</strong> The Cost of items can be hidden. See <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933312043/Hiding+Analytics+on+Tickets+and+Price+Checks\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933312043\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Hiding Cost on VCT/Price Check</a> for additional information.</p><p /><p>4. Clicking the Catalog Item link will take you to the Inventory Summary for the item.</p><p>Alternatively, click the <strong>X\u00a0</strong>button to close the window and return to your previous page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279488/Price%20Check%203.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933279488/Price%20Check%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
